	<text>
		<body>
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001924_0001"><!--pb/@n='32r'--></pb>
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName><geogName type="cataract">Cataracts</geogName></placeName> <date when="1863-06-02">2 June  
<lb/>1863</date></p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My dear <persName><choice><abbr>HW</abbr><expan>Horace Waller</expan></choice></persName></p>
<lb/><p>I send the 
<lb/>brass wire you 
<lb/>requested by the 
<lb/><orgName><placeName><settlement type="city">Senna</settlement></placeName> men</orgName> who 
<lb/>came with the 
<lb/><term type="animal">cattle</term> and hope it 
<lb/>will serve your 
<lb/>purpose.</p>
<lb/><p>We have your 
<lb/><term type="animal">bulls</term> to break 
<lb/>in - the <term type="animal">cows</term> 
<lb/>unfortunately 

     

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001924_0002"><!--pb/@n='32v'--></pb>
<lb/>ran dry in the 
<lb/>way. but our 
<lb/><placeName><geogName type="island">Johanna</geogName></placeName> <term type="animal">cows</term> 
<lb/>send to promise 
<lb/>better things.</p>
<lb/><p>You did not 
<lb/>mention whether 
<lb/>you had "<bibl>All the 
<lb/>year round</bibl>" or not 
<lb/>I am afraid our 
<lb/>worthy <term type="occupation">seamen</term> 
<lb/>may have made 
<lb/>off with it.  

     

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001924_0003"><!--pb/@n='33r'--></pb>
<lb/>If I were not tired 
<lb/>with writing vile 
<lb/>Portuguese I might 
<lb/>congratulate you 
<lb/>on the sympathy 
<lb/>some folks <choice><orig>shew</orig><reg>show</reg></choice> 
<lb/>you in reference 
<lb/>to the <orgName><hi rend="underline">mission</hi></orgName>
<lb/>people behaving 
<lb/>so badly.  The 
<lb/>weather is <w>com<supplied>-</supplied><lb break="no"/>pletely</w> changed I 
<lb/>think - 49ยบ here 
<lb/>this morning &amp; 
<lb/>our general health 

     

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001924_0004"><!--pb/@n='33v'--></pb>
<lb/>is improving - I hope 
<lb/><persName>Procter</persName> will soon 
<lb/>be himself again 
<lb/>with kind salutations 
<lb/>to <persName>Rowley</persName> I am &amp;c</p>
<lb/><p rend="right"><persName><choice><abbr>D</abbr><expan>David</expan></choice> Livingstone</persName></p>
			
</div>
